column1: Availability of Data in NBER World Trade Data Base
1. French Indian Ocean Territories include Comoros, French South Antartic Territories, and Reunion.
3. St. Kt-Nev-An includes Antigua and Barbuda, British Virgin Islands,
Dominica, Grenada, Montserrat, Former St. Kitts/Nev/Anguilla (until 1980),
St. Kitts and Nevis, Anguilla, St. Lucia, and St. Vincent and the Grenadines.
4. US NES includes Former Pacific Islands (until 1991), Micronesia, Federal
States of, Marshall Islands, Palau and US Miscellaneous Pacific Islands.
5. Asia NES includes Bhutan and Brunei Darussalam.
6. EEC NES refers to European Union Not Elsewhere Specified.
7. Import data for Russian Federation (1992-1995) are missing.
